        "product_description": {
            "value": "The ASR Outdoor FCB-2110 Thin Flexible Kitchen Cutting Board is a versatile chopping mat designed for everyday kitchen use. Measuring 15\"L x 12\"W, this lightweight, flexible cutting board makes food prep simple and mess-free. Its thin, bendable design allows you to easily fold the mat and pour chopped ingredients directly into a pan, bowl, or pot without spilling. Made from durable, food-safe plastic, this clear cutting board provides a smooth, stable surface for slicing fruits, vegetables, meats, and fish. The flexible material is gentle on knife edges while remaining sturdy enough for repeated use. Ideal for separating raw and cooked foods to help reduce cross-contamination, these mats are a practical addition to any kitchen. Cleanup is effortless — each board is dishwasher safe and quick to rinse by hand. This convenient 20-pack ensures you always have a fresh, clean surface on hand, making them perfect for busy households, meal prep, outdoor cooking, and camping. Compact and easy to store, the boards stack neatly in a drawer or cabinet. Whether you're preparing a family dinner or packing for an outdoor adventure, the ASR Outdoor Thin Flexible Cutting Board delivers reliable performance and lasting value.",
            "is_required": true,
            "source": "ai",
            "model": "claude-opus-4-8"
